  "Description": {
    "English": "A sinister shard of <span class=\"name name-special\">purple glass</span>, salvaged from the destroyed remains of Sentinel machinery. Its walls are thin, and it may be broken down to access valuable Sentinel components.<br><br>Select in the Inventory (<span class=\"name name-img\">INVENTORY</span>) and shatter with <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-special\">紫色玻璃</span>构成的不详碎片，来自被摧毁的护卫机体残骸。外壁极其轻薄，打破后也许能够提供宝贵的护卫构件。<br><br>在库存（<span class=\"name name-img\">INVENTORY</span>）中选择碎片并按<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>将其打破。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一塊邪惡的<span class=\"name name-special\">紫色玻璃</span>碎片，從被毀壞的巡警機械殘骸中回收而來。它的外壁很薄，也許可以被分解成珍貴的巡警元件。<br><br>在道具欄 (<span class=\"name name-img\">INVENTORY</span>) 中選擇並按下<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>分解。"
  },
